item.title: Lorem Ipsum
item.dc:creator: admin
item.description: Martin: What’s with all the strange looking words on some of these posts and pages? Julius: It’s Latin. Martin: Ah. […]
item.content:encoded:
Martin:

What’s with all the strange looking words on some of these posts and pages?

Julius:

It’s Latin.

Martin:

Ah. Do you read Latin?

Julius:

Not a word.

Martin:

That’s pretty weird then, isn’t it?

Julius:

Nope, it’s just there as filler text.

Martin:

Like breadcrumbs in meatloaf.

Julius:

Sort of, I guess.
